  "muayeneEkleYavruYokTaniBaslik": "No-Brood Short Diagnostic Observations",
  "muayeneEkleYavruYokTaniAciklama": "This section does not select a diagnosis. The system reads these 4 simple observations together with current season, process window and colony strength to produce recommendations.",
  "muayeneEkleTaniKoloniSakin": "Is the colony calm?",
  "muayeneEkleTaniKoloniSakinAciklama": "A calm colony increases the probability of a new queen inside. A restless colony raises suspicion of queenlessness/stress.",
  "muayeneEkleTaniPolen": "Is there pollen coming in?",
  "muayeneEkleTaniPolenAciklama": "Pollen input supports the probability of brood preparation or queen presence inside. Absence of pollen increases the risk of biological stagnation.",
  "muayeneEkleTaniBal": "Is honey / nectar flow strong?",
  "muayeneEkleTaniBalAciklama": "Strong flow can narrow the laying area. In this case, absence of brood may not directly mean queenlessness.",
  "muayeneEkleTaniErkek": "Are drone brood cells dominant?",
  "muayeneEkleTaniErkekAciklama": "If yes, the risk of unmated queen, failed queen or laying worker increases. This answer hardens the waiting decision.",
  "muayeneEkleTaniEminDegil": "Not sure",

